html:
12.7.21  12:49 am   Can I interview you one day?

      sure

12.7.21  12:38 am   why am i scared of butterflies 

      because they are huge

12.7.21  12:01 am   Do you tend to work on the lyrics or music first? 

      absolutely not

12.6.21  11:54 pm   How do you figure out what to make a song sound like?

      it's impossible. no one knows what it should sound like

12.6.21  11:33 pm   what do you do when you get a repeat question?

      i have 3 different ways of dealing with that. 1: skip it, 2: answer it the same way i've answered it before, or 3: answer it in a different way than i've answered it before

12.6.21  8:39 pm   favorite holiday?

      'today'

12.6.21  5:12 pm   can you make a class with one of its arguments being a class object itself in python

      i'm not sure

12.6.21  4:51 pm   what can you name 59 of

      numbers

12.6.21  4:46 pm   if you raise the pitch of you voice at the end of something does it make it a question?

      not exactly

12.6.21  3:09 pm   what do you think about often

      time

12.6.21  1:53 pm   what do you do when you fail

      something wrong, apparently

12.6.21  11:01 am   how to deal with (existential) dread

      start putting together a stage show

12.6.21  10:19 am   do you get tired of answering the same questions over and over

      no, each one makes me more awake

12.6.21  9:10 am   when did all the windmills start to turn so slow

      they have been spinning at the same speed this entire time, but your emotional perception of time may have changed

12.6.21  8:53 am   why did you use single letters to represent things in your previous videos?

for example, you used the letter b to represent a boat in "got some money" and the letter t to represent the truth in "more than a dream"

      it's easy and fun

12.6.21  2:00 am   do we need to invent a lowerer case to be more casual?

      no. the secret to casual communication is to use the path of least resistance

12.6.21  1:02 am   why are you cool?

      must be some kind of paranoid strategy to get people to like me

12.5.21  11:35 pm   What font is it that you use in every video you make

      regular

12.5.21  10:50 pm   will i ever be fixed?

      yes

12.5.21  10:07 pm   is memorizing the greek alphabet a reliable way to look smart

      no

12.5.21  9:46 pm   why are you're songs good

      must be some kind of paranoid strategy to get people to like me

12.5.21  9:12 pm   My best friend believes human civilization will collapse in 2040 and there's nothing we can do to stop it. Do you agree?

      no

12.5.21  9:01 pm   Many of your music videos show you playing a nonexistent drumset; however, the placement and motions shown would suggest that you have ample practice playing a real drumset. Is this true?

      yes

12.5.21  8:07 pm   favorite time of the day? 

      i like when the time changes. that's the only thing that does it for me anymore

12.5.21  7:07 pm   opinion on the sky

      it's good

12.5.21  2:27 pm   does your next music video have videos with you singing and dancing in it

      i'm thinking that would be the best option

12.5.21  2:19 pm   what is your favorite number

      1 or 2

12.5.21  11:52 am   Fav youtuber?

      what the heck is a youtuber

12.5.21  8:35 am   We know the first 62,831,853,071,750 digits of pi, thanks to supercomputers. What do you feel about this?

      i feel fairly calm about it

12.5.21  6:38 am   Who do you think will be world chess champion?

      you might have to do it

12.5.21  5:45 am   are the dreams in more than a dream and i'm a princess connected in meaning?

      they are both connected to my overuse of the word dream

12.5.21  3:21 am   do you have any songs that do the kind of traditional "modulate up a semitone or 2 at the end of the song" type of key change?

      i must have done it but i can't think of any examples

12.5.21  2:10 am   when you are in an airport terminal, do you sometimes think about "zhszwhzhszhwhzhzhwhsh" planes landing? cuz I do

      i was going to say no but now that i think about it yes

12.4.21  11:53 pm   why do you randomly wear glasses sometimes in your videos and are these real glasses 

      sometimes i use wardrobe changes as a way to offset the fact that every person on screen the same person

12.4.21  10:36 pm   why dont i use capital letters?

      maybe you discovered that your writing is still very readable without it, maybe even more straightforward and honest

12.4.21  9:59 pm   my spoon is acting weird how do I make it stop?

      how about destroying the entire universe

12.4.21  9:41 pm   why are problems solved by not being solved?

      because it escalates the need for them to be solved, and makes it more likely that someone will want to solve it

12.4.21  9:40 pm   How is your day?

      light

12.4.21  9:37 pm   this is kind of a weird question but basically... um, i was going through a bunch of stuff about losing friends and being worried everybody hated me, and at the end of all of that, i subconsiously put on more than a dream and thought about the lyrics really hard. i might be looking too far into it, but that song isn't about dreams at all, is it? 

      most songs are about everything

12.4.21  5:05 pm   opinion on canada

      rectangular projection makes it look way bigger than it is, but, despite this fact, it is still huge

12.4.21  12:36 pm   what's your favorite part of the color spectrum?

      when it changes

      "gifts on the trees" is short for "there's decorations on the trees and there's also gifts nearby"

12.4.21  10:51 am   How big is the universe?

      sizeless

12.4.21  8:20 am   will you use the letter "f" to represent fear in your next video?

      i don't think so

12.3.21  11:55 pm   you remind me of someone but I can't remember who? Who could it be?

      you?

12.3.21  10:43 pm   How do you feel about people interpreting your lyrics in ways you may not have intended them?

      as long as it's with the music then it's probably fine

12.3.21  10:26 pm   How would humans quantify anything if mathematics wasn't useful in describing the physical world? 

      in that case they wouldn't need to

12.3.21  10:15 pm   Which is harder: Animation or writing the song?

      animation but there's a 3rd part which goes in between those two parts and that's recording the song

12.3.21  8:31 pm   What kind of books do you enjoy?

      i like when they put the front cover on the back

12.3.21  7:42 pm   What chord would you use to represent your life right now?

      i need at least 2 chords to represent anything living
